Package ca.polymtl.inf3995.oronos.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DrawerActivity
    Drawer Activity The Drawer Activity is in charge of the hamburger menu that allows the user to switch between the application themes, to choose a PDF for download, to disconnect itself and last but not least to set the receiving rocket data mode.
    HomeScreenActivity
    Home Screen Activity The Home Screen Activity is in charge of displaying a user log in questionnaire of three input fields: username, password and server IP address.
    HomeScreenActivity.BasicErrorListener
    Listener for the error responses that can occur when trying to log in the user.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigBasicListener
    Listener for the response to a get basic configuration request.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigCanDataTypesListener
    Listener for the response to a get can data types request.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigCanModuleTypesListener
    Listener for the response to a get module types request.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigCanMsgDataTypesListener
    Listener for the response to a get can msg data types request.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigCanSidListener
    Listener for the response to a get can sid configuration request.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigRocketsListener
    Listener for the response to a get rocket configuration request.
    HomeScreenActivity.GetConfigTimeoutListener
    Listener for the response to a get module types request.
    HomeScreenActivity.PostUsersLoginListener
    Listener for the response to a user log in request.
    MainActivity
    Main Activity The Main Activity is in charge of switching between the views containing the rocket data.
    PdfActivity
    Pdf Activity The Pdf Activity is responsible of managing the PDF list the client gets from the server and to provocate PDF downloads that are requested by the user.
